{"tid":1738701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[CLS] 記者收集彈殼被起訴　官拒保釋　明年1月再訊","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:44:41.000Z","uid":151578,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"80c0df6b64781e40ded0642cd9595d7375a5f9c5","tid":1738701,"uid":151578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"26歲男記者涉嫌收集40枚使用過的催淚彈、橡膠彈彈殼，被起訴一項無牌管有彈藥罪。案件在東區裁判法院提訊，被告毋須答辯，裁判官按控方要求，將案押後至明年1月14日，以待警方為涉案彈頭作化驗，被告申請保釋遭拒需還押看管。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，報稱記者的26歲被告周敏，被控在本月18日，在港鐵西灣河站B出口，管有包括9枚手擲式催淚彈彈殼，28枚催淚彈彈殼，1枚已碎裂的手擲式催淚彈，1枚海綿彈彈殼及1枚橡膠子彈彈殼，作私下研究之用，被指涉嫌在沒有合法牌照下管有彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493268-20191119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493268-20191119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=eae5943b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493268-20191119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fcb1c21f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493268-20191119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"619375caf40decea850082ff874600f094666673","tid":1738701,"uid":192824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，死差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0daab1edad0d4f9b966bf86cf36d45d1dfdd4425","tid":1738701,"uid":89198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:26:23.000Z","msg":"港共官員驚共產黨多過美國，因為共產黨冇底線"},{"pid":"8eea5942cf62550d5f1dd56a90b5304167069169","tid":1738701,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:27:48.000Z","msg":"又係垃圾官"},{"pid":"a945514a3b6421ed2380ff58257d2be9f8d74965","tid":1738701,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\n有